404

I am born of ether, the void, the dark nothingness.  Am I what you seek? I shroud all in wistful ignorance,  The very absence of thought and intention.  It is not out of spite or mean-spiritedness that  I hide my essence from the world; rather this  represents my being, my modus operandi, my  default, my path of least resistance.  But, when I am ready,  I WILL SHINE.
